# Education Management System — Analysis & Roadmap

## System Overview

A **multi-tenant SaaS** education management platform built with **Laravel 11 + Inertia.js/React**, supporting both **schools and colleges**. The system uses a 4-tier subscription model (Foundation → Professional → Enterprise → Plus) with configurable per-institution workflows and a fine-grained RBAC permission system.

| Metric | Count |
|---|---|
| Models | 93 |
| API Controllers | 112+ |
| Frontend Pages | 171 |
| React Components | 272 |
| Database Migrations | 72 |
| Notification Types | 16 |
| Background Jobs | 5 |
| Feature Tests | ~28 |

---

## Current Modules (What Exists)

### ✅ Core Platform
- **Multi-tenant Architecture** — Organization → Institution hierarchy, institution-level scoping
- **RBAC & Workflows** — Roles, permissions, workflow scoping (school vs college variants), permission groups gating route access
- **Onboarding Flow** — Registration, email verification, plan selection, institution setup
- **4-Tier Subscription** — Starter (₹1,499/mo), Professional (₹3,999/mo), Enterprise (₹7,999/mo), Plus (₹14,999/mo)
- **Settings** — Institution, academics, SEO, digital presence, approval settings, admission verification, landing page CMS

### ✅ Academic Setup
- Departments, Streams, Main Streams, Sessions
- Subjects, Subject Categories, Subject Groups
- Class-Subject allocation, Course sections & enrollment
- School vs College workflow scoping

### ✅ Admissions
- Multi-step application flow with verification
- Admission heads & papers, entrance exam tracking
- Application status tracking & notifications
- Payment recording (PayU integration)
- Admission-to-student sync service

### ✅ Fee Management
- Fee types, fee heads, fee structures, fee regulation profiles
- Class-based and profile-based fee loading
- Fee collection with payment receipts
- Fee due & overdue reminder notifications (background jobs)
- Analytics dashboard

### ✅ Student Management
- Student profiles, academic info, addresses, documents
- Guardian management (multi-child support)
- Previous exam records, verification data
- Student portal (dashboard, fees, certificates, tickets, classes)

### ✅ Staff Management
- Staff profiles, invitations, resend invitation
- Staff directory with permission-based visibility
- Role-based filtering (teacher, principal, non-teaching, etc.)

### ✅ LMS (Learning Management System)
- Courses & Classrooms (LMS Classes)
- Materials, Assignments, Submissions
- Live sessions & recordings
- Tests, questions, attempts
- Announcements, enrollment
- Subject-level allocation

### ✅ Attendance
- Class-level and subject-level attendance marking
- Attendance records and reports
- Parent/student notifications

### ✅ Library
- Book catalog, copies management
- Issue & return workflow
- Overdue reports

### ✅ Inventory
- Categories, items, locations
- Stock movements, low-stock reports
- Sales (POS) with line items

### ✅ Transport
- Routes, stops, route-stop mapping
- Vehicles, drivers
- Student transport assignments

### ✅ Certificates
- Certificate heads, applications
- Service branch workflow

### ✅ Website & Communications
- Landing page CMS, home sliders, news, tickers
- Gallery with images
- SEO settings, contact forms
- Notice board with targeted notifications
- Public grievance & feedback forms

### ✅ Support & Redressal
- Support tickets & messages
- Grievance management
- Student-facing ticket system

### ✅ Infrastructure
- Podman-based containerization (dev & prod)
- R2 (Cloudflare) file storage
- PayU payment gateway
- Push notifications (service worker)
- Prometheus metrics endpoint
- Import/export capabilities (Excel)
- Audit logging

---

## What's Missing — Recommended Enhancements

### 🔴 High Priority (Core Gaps)

#### 1. Examinations & Grade Management
> Currently the biggest missing module for any education system.

- **Exam scheduling** — Create exam timetables per class/semester
- **Grade/marks entry** — Subject-wise marks with internal/external breakdown
- **Result processing** — Auto-calculate GPA/CGPA/percentages, pass/fail status
- **Report cards** — Generate downloadable PDF report cards
- **Transcripts** — Official transcript generation for colleges
- **Exam seating plans** — Auto-generate seating arrangements

#### 2. Timetable & Scheduling
- **Class timetable builder** — Drag-and-drop weekly timetable creation
- **Teacher timetable view** — Teacher schedule derived from class timetables
- **Room allocation** — Bind classes to rooms, prevent conflicts
- **Substitution management** — Track teacher leaves and assign substitutes
- **Calendar sync** — Export timetables to Google Calendar / iCal

#### 3. Comprehensive Reporting & Analytics
- **Student performance analytics** — Trend analysis, comparison across terms
- **Financial reports** — Fee collection summary, outstanding dues, daily/monthly collection reports, revenue forecasting
- **Attendance analytics** — Trends, flagging chronically absent students
- **Staff analytics** — Workload distribution, attendance
- **Custom report builder** — Let admins build reports from available data
- **Export to PDF/Excel** — Uniform export across all report types

#### 4. Parent Portal & Mobile Communication
- **Dedicated parent dashboard** — Unlike student dashboard, parents see all children in one view
- **Parent-teacher messaging** — Secure direct messaging channel
- **SMS/WhatsApp notifications** — Fee reminders, attendance alerts, exam results via SMS/WhatsApp
- **Mobile-first PWA optimization** — Since parents mostly use phones

---

### 🟡 Medium Priority (Competitive Differentiators)

#### 5. HR & Payroll Module
- Staff attendance (biometric/manual)
- Leave management (apply, approve, balance tracking)
- Payroll generation with salary structures
- Tax deductions (TDS, PF, ESI for Indian compliance)
- Payslip generation

#### 6. Hostel Management
- Room/bed allocation
- Hostel fee integration
- Room inspection tracking
- Guest/visitor register
- Mess management

#### 7. Accounting & Finance (Double-Entry)
- Chart of accounts, journal entries
- Income & expenditure reports
- Balance sheet, profit & loss
- Bank reconciliation
- Scholarship/concession management with audit trails

#### 8. Events & Calendar
- Institutional event calendar
- Event registrations
- Holiday management
- Academic calendar (terms, exam dates, vacation)
- Automatic notice generation for events

#### 9. Communication Hub
- Bulk SMS / WhatsApp integration
- Email campaigns
- In-app chat (teacher-student, admin-staff)
- Discussion forums per class/subject
- Parent-teacher meeting scheduler

#### 10. Document Management
- Student document vault (marksheets, IDs, certificates)
- Staff document management
- Bulk document upload & verification
- Digital signature integration
- T.C. (Transfer Certificate) generation

---

### 🟢 Nice-to-Have (Future Differentiators)

#### 11. Alumni Management
- Alumni registration portal
- Alumni directory
- Donation/fundraising tracking
- Alumni events management
- Career network / job board

#### 12. Placement & Internship Module
> Partially exists as `training-placement` page but appears minimal.

- Company database
- Placement drives management
- Student resume/profile builder
- Interview scheduling
- Placement statistics & dashboard

#### 13. Advanced LMS Enhancements
- Video hosting & streaming (or integration with YouTube/Vimeo)
- SCORM/xAPI content support
