- AISHE data submission
- UDISE+ compliance (for schools)
- Configurable compliance checklists
- Document readiness tracker for inspections

#### 15. Advanced Security & Governance
- **SSO integration** (listed in Enterprise tier but not implemented)
- API access for third-party integration
- Data retention policies
- GDPR/data privacy compliance tools
- IP-based access restrictions

