## Technical Debt & Infrastructure Improvements

| Area | Current State | Recommendation |
|---|---|---|
| **Test Coverage** | ~28 feature tests, minimal unit tests | Increase to 70%+ coverage, add integration tests for fee/admission flows |
| **API Documentation** | None visible | Add Swagger/OpenAPI spec, auto-generated from routes |
| **Error Monitoring** | Not visible | Add Sentry/Bugsnag integration |
| **Performance** | No visible caching layer | Add Redis caching for dashboard queries, permission resolution |
| **Search** | Basic queries | Add full-text search (Meilisearch/Algolia) for students, books, inventory |
| **CI/CD** | `.github` exists (12 items) | Ensure full pipeline: lint → test → build → deploy |
| **i18n** | Not present | Add multi-language support (Hindi, regional languages) |
| **Accessibility** | Unknown | Audit WCAG 2.1 AA compliance |
| **Rate Limiting** | Partial (auth routes only) | Extend to all API endpoints |
| **Backup & Recovery** | Not visible | Automated database backups with point-in-time recovery |

